      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TALCOTT BALE (2) has missed the placings at his last couple but was in the money three back when third (25.25) at Shepparton in a Special conditions H. Has the ability and expected to go close. PAW IMPERIAL (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (29.97) at this track behind Typhoon Baylee in a Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Expected to be in the finish again. PAW WINKWORTH (3) was safely held in tougher company last start after settling off pace at this track, but prior to that won by 1.3 lengths at this track (29.51) beating Warm Hugs in a Grade 5 on March 19. Great chance to atone. PAW FABIAN (7) can feature with the right run.",
